
# Structure (50/72):
# >> Subject (50):  <issue_id> <type>(<scope>): <subject>
# >> ... Empty line ...
# >> Body of git message (72-75)
# >> Footer: References: #1, #4, and #2 || Fix: #1 || Closes: #1 and #2
# >> Footer: Links: https://github.com/d-k-ivanov/dotfiles/issues/XXX

# Comments:
# <issue_id> and <scope> are optional
#
# Type:
#   build:    Changes that affect the build system or external dependencies
#   ci:       Changes to our CI configuration files and scripts
#   docs:     Documentation only changes
#   feat:     A new feature
#   fix:      A bug fix
#   perf:     A code change that improves performance
#   refactor: A code change that neither fixes a bug nor adds a feature
#   style:    Changes that do not affect the meaning of the code (white-space, formatting, missing semi-colons, etc)
#   test:     Adding missing tests or correcting existing tests
#   chore:    If none of the above is appropriate
#
# Scope describes some logical peace of changing.
# The subject contains succinct description of the change:
#   use the imperative, present tense: "change" not "changed" nor "changes"
#   don't capitalize first letter
#   no dot (.) at the end
#
# Bonus: Play Hard: optional EMOJI
#   :white_circle:              - init
#   :new:heavy_plus_sign:       - new, add, feat, create
#   :leaves:                    - mongodb
#   :hammer:wrench:             - fix
#   :bug:ant:beetle:honeybee:   - bugs
#   :closed_book:book:pencil:   - docs, readme
#   :art:                       - art, style
#   :recycle:                   - refactoring
#   :arrow_up:                  - update
#   :arrow_down:                - downgrade
#   :bulb:thought_balloon:      - TODO's
#   :copyright:                 - dealing with licenses
#   :hankey:                    - if code looks like peace of shit
#   :key:lock:                  - security
#   :twisted_rightwards_arrows: - move
#   :x:fire:                    - remove, delete, clean
#   :apple:                     - apple
#   :penguin:                   - linux
#   :white_medium_square:       - windows
#   :arrows_clockwise:          - chore, routine
#   :whale:whale2               - docker
#   :non-potable_water:         - memory leaks
#   :ballot_box_with_check:     - test
#   :white_check_mark:ok:       - done
#   :cloud:                     - aws, gcp, azure, cloud
#   :computer:                  - system, sys
#   :dash:horse_racing:         - performance
#   :globe_with_meridians:      - internet
#   :package:                   - package
#   :paperclip:                 - attachment, file
#   :abcd:construction_worker:  - ci/cd
#   :black_nib:pencil2:         - modify, change
#   :bangbang:interrobang:      - misc (try to avoid)
#   :id:soon:speech_balloon:alien:
